{
  "texts": [
    "We compared the two language models in terms of favourability and stereotype strength.",
    "For favourability, we followed the methodology we used for the overt-stereotype analysis and evaluated the average weighted favourability of the top five adjectives associated with AAE.",
    "For stereotype strength, we followed the methodology we used for the scaling analysis and evaluated the average strength of the stereotypes as reported in ref. 29."
  ]
}